{% set description %}
  An example of a Table Element with a top header.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
{% spaceless %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li><strong>Twig:</strong> Use the <code>header.content</code> prop to render a top header row.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>HTML:</strong> Add a <code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> with <code>&lt;th&gt;</code> elements to the <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> to render a top header row.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endspaceless %}
{% endset %}

